  <brief_title>Mortality of Severe Sepsis at 30 Days Before/After Implementation of Prescription Tool</brief_title>
  <official_title>EVALUATION OF 30-DAY MORTALITY AFTER A VISIT TO THE LAPEYRONIE ADULT EMERGENCY DEPARTMENT OF THE CHU MONTPELLIER FOR SEPSIS OR SEPTIC SHOCK: A STUDY BEFORE/AFTER THE IMPLEMENTATION OF AN ANTI-INFECTIOUS PRESCRIPTION AID</official_title>
