  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Anti-infective strategy is a major public health problem. This is a before-and-after study of&#xD;
      an anti-infectious prescription tool with a comparison of mortality at 30 days (then 3 and 6&#xD;
      months) between the two inclusion phases of 6 months each.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
